entityClassTypeListeners

java.util.Map<K,V> entityClassTypeListeners
A map with to hold entity listeners for specific kind of classes. It will be later used to add these listeners to newly added entities in the context service.

entitySpecificListenerWrappers

java.util.Set<E> entitySpecificListenerWrappers
A map to keep track of all the listeners belonging to a specific entity in the context service. This might be a bit of an overload, but since this class is the one introducing one level of indirection (wrap the listener) it's its responsibility to keep track and then an properly remove the correct listener on request!
